:<!--Trigger PerformanceE 202030714: Config/Level/Mission/2020307/Act/Act202030714.json-->
:{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 113.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' Where did Yunshen get to, I asked him to watch the shop while I used my voucher... He's often hanging around here &mdash; always seemed nice enough. *sigh* Not trustworthy after all.
:{{A|VO side2 lc1 mar7th 189.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' That crook wanted to cheat us out of 500 strales.
:{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 114.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' What? You didn't give him the money, did you?
:{{A|VO side2 lc1 mar7th 190.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Of course not! We scared him off.
:{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 115.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' You two are incredible. I'll have to have a word with him later... Ugh, asking him to help was my mistake &mdash; I apologize.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} No worries! You weren't to know.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202071707-->
::{{A|VO side2 lc1 mar7th 191.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' That's right. Making mistakes is part of growing up.
::{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 116.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' Here &mdash; a little something for the inconvenience. It's yummy.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} It was a bit of a goof, huh...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202071710-->
::{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 117.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' Mm-hmm, I won't be so quick to leave my post in the future.
::{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 118.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' Here &mdash; a little something for the inconvenience. It's yummy.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_202071712-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202071712-->
:{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 119.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' It'd be best if Mr. Xiyan didn't find out about this... He doesn't show up very often, but he's the manager here. I'll be in big trouble if he finds out what happened.
:{{A|VO side2 lc1 mar7th 192.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Don't worry, we can keep a secret. Just make sure it doesn't happen again!
----
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
