:<!--Trigger PerformanceE 202030721: Config/Level/Mission/2020307/Act/Act202030721.json-->
:{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 120.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' Where did Yunshen get to, I asked him to watch the shop while I used my voucher... He's often hanging around here &mdash; always seemed nice enough. *sigh* Not trustworthy after all.
:{{A|VO side2 lc1 mar7th 193.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' That crook cheated us out of 500 strales.
:{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 121.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' What!? I apologize, this is my fault &mdash; I'll have a word with him later. Let me give you your money back first.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} No need, you couldn't have known this would happen.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202071805-->
::{{A|VO side2 lc1 mar7th 194.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Yeah, it's his problem, not yours.
::{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 122.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' *sigh* At the end of the day, this wouldn't have happened if I'd stayed at my post.
::{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 123.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' Here &mdash; a little something for the inconvenience. It's yummy.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Thanks very much.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202071809-->
::{{A|VO side2 lc1 mar7th 195.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Hey, you're gonna take it!? Yinshu, this isn't your fault &mdash; you don't have to do this.
::{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 124.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' *sigh* At the end of the day, this wouldn't have happened if I'd stayed at my post.
::{{A|VO side2 lc1 mar7th 196.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' This is your hard-earned money. Looking after a bookshop is no easy task.
::{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 125.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' Th&mdash;Thanks... In that case, have this instead &mdash; it's tasty.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_202071813-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202071813-->
:{{A|VO side2 lc1 mar7th 197.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Aw, that's so kind of you! You just made a loyal customer out of me.
:{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 126.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' Glad to hear that! Please come by anytime!
:{{A|VO side2 lc1 yinshu 127.ogg}} '''Yinshu:''' It'd be best if Mr. Xiyan didn't find out about this... He doesn't show up very often, but he's the manager here. I'll be in big trouble if he finds out what happened.
:{{A|VO side2 lc1 mar7th 198.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Don't worry, we can keep a secret. Just make sure it doesn't happen again!
----
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
